    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but isn't that a bit dangerous though? if we say conscience is more important than the law, doesn't that pretty much give any group an excuse to ignore any law they don't like? like, where does it stop? if we prioritize religious exemptions over the secular state, aren't we basically just admitting that the law doesn't actually apply to everyone equally?",
